    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><br>进入激烈的激光坦克世界，在与敌人进行无情的战斗中成功完成复苏地球的任务。参与具有挑战性的俯视射击体验。在各种环境中与外星怪物和对手坦克进行史诗般的战斗。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/29a37dd0cb38ba80a171a0151a073a69.poster.avif?t=1769600208\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/29a37dd0cb38ba80a171a0151a073a69.webm?t=1769600208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/29a37dd0cb38ba80a171a0151a073a69.mp4?t=1769600208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事</h2><br>时代是2150年，来自神秘危险世界的外星人窃取了整个地球赖以生存的关键半导体芯片。如今，地球的命运掌握在你手中，你必须接受挑战，恢复它的昔日辉煌。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/24875aa6e49b521a691b9c83ee38ce77.poster.avif?t=1769600208\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/24875aa6e49b521a691b9c83ee38ce77.webm?t=1769600208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/24875aa6e49b521a691b9c83ee38ce77.mp4?t=1769600208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 可以使用多种武器击败外星怪物。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/8f91281bad574d0e120c3f49e2388c75.poster.avif?t=1769600208\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/8f91281bad574d0e120c3f49e2388c75.webm?t=1769600208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/8f91281bad574d0e120c3f49e2388c75.mp4?t=1769600208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> 使用配备强大激光的各种激光坦克摧毁外星怪物。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/b1cd251e070ca9bad48d6ca70bd2459f.poster.avif?t=1769600208\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/b1cd251e070ca9bad48d6ca70bd2459f.webm?t=1769600208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/b1cd251e070ca9bad48d6ca70bd2459f.mp4?t=1769600208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> 体验令人惊叹的各种环境，如黑暗森林、地下城、科幻等。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/21c6836fdee1789909249a11367b020f.poster.avif?t=1769600208\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/21c6836fdee1789909249a11367b020f.webm?t=1769600208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/21c6836fdee1789909249a11367b020f.mp4?t=1769600208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> 完成各种任务，如停用闭路电视摄像头，使用PIN码解锁等。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/afee415285c76785b9bddc796d3f5869.poster.avif?t=1769600208\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/afee415285c76785b9bddc796d3f5869.webm?t=1769600208\" type=\"vid